passkey_button_matched_text:
Experience "Passkeys" Login
What Are
Passkeys utilize public key cryptography techniques where a matched set of public and private keys, rather than a password or passphrase, is used to authenticate a user's identity.
User-friendly login

Elevate your app's user experience by logging users in with their facial ID or fingerprints.

Phishing-proof

Public-private key pairs only work with the intended application, thwarting any credential phishing attempts.

MFA simplified

Passkeys check both possession (device) and inherence (biometrics) without an extra step.

Want To Add Passkeys To Your App?
Descope helps developers easily add any passwordless authentication method (like Passkeys) to their apps with a few lines of code. Choose from our drag-and-drop workflows, SDKs, or APIs.
Sign Up

MyFairfax Login

MyFairfax is your home to conduct key online transactions with the county. This is an ongoing customer service initiative to provide you with faster and easier access to your county information in a secure environment.

Residents have direct access to their Personal Property (Car) Tax, Business Personal Property Tax, and Real Estate Tax information.

In addition to tax information, Circuit Court records from 1742 onwards are offered through a subscriber-based service called CPAN. Subscribers for this service, typically include land professionals, such as title examiners, law offices, mortgage companies, banks, Commissioner of Accounts and county agencies. To register for CPAN, please refer to the Court Public Access Network overview page and submit an application to receive a User ID for access.

Register for an account today or login to view your information. If you have questions/suggestions/feedback, please email MyFairfax Help.
